### Preview Service Test Endpoints

### Generate Preview for a Project
POST http://localhost:8080/api/preview/generate/test-project-123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Preview Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/preview/status/test-project-123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Cleanup Preview
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/preview/cleanup/test-project-123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_TOKEN_HERE

